rows.label: tlk45310341_01_msg0002
rows.name:
That's the name of the mercenary band
Vandham runs, and it's also what we
call this village where we all live.

rows.label: tlk45310341_01_msg0003
rows.name:
As you can see, we take all sorts here.
Mercenaries and Drivers from all over
Alst, and plenty of kids too.

rows.label: tlk45310341_01_msg0004
rows.name: Naturally, you're welcome here as well.
